Rattrap:



Rattrap took out what ever he could find under his subspace pocket 
under armor. He manged to take out dead detionator controlers, a 
wrench, a flashlight head, and old empty containers. Quickstrike had 
taken all his weapons. Even his sticky bombs. 

He sat back and eyed the panel that had the on and off button of the 
confinements. He picked up a few of the objects and began to throw 
them against the panel, hoping that he could hit it.
